'''Domain Fath''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Intendant caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. They had many high ranking [[Consul/Legends|Consuls]] among their number. Because of their influence, one of their own, [[Bhu Fath]], was made a [[Commander/Legends|Commander]], despite his obvious incompetence.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

